---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Module 1 — Savoring Life | Events">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/events/module-1-hero.png" alt="" class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-85" loading="eager" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/85 via-black/55 to-black"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 pb-10 pt-14 md:pb-14 md:pt-20">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/70">Events / Savoring Life / Module 1</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold text-white md:text-6xl">Module 1: Savoring Life</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-white/80">“The Art of Flavor and Awareness”</p>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-white/75">
        Flavor is both literal and metaphorical: by tuning into the senses, we train attention and learn to
        receive life more deeply—because richness isn’t only what we consume, but how we receive it.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/contact" class="rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white no-underline hover:bg-white/15">
          Host Module 1 (inquire)
        </a>
        <a href="/events/savoring-life" class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white/80 no-underline hover:bg-white/5">
          Back to Season
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 pb-14 pt-10">
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">Body</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Sensation → awareness</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          Mindful chewing, pauses between bites, sensory nuance, and the gut–brain axis.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">Mind</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Attention expands experience</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          Novelty + attention expand perceived flavor; noticing refines memory and meaning.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">Spirit</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Gratitude as practice</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          Savoring as gratitude—taste with reverence, including the “bitter” parts of life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
